BEYOND the DARKNESS hears tales of The Devil's Board & Other Shocking Stories of the Supernatural with guest L. Syndey Fisher

Novelist L. Sydney Fisher bases her supernatural books on actual cases, she has had a lifetime of paranormal encounters and she digs deep into others claims sharing them with us today.

Get her books here: www.Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio

Visit her website here:
http://www.lsydneyfisher.com/
